---
title: Easy Smokey Chicken & Creamy Slaw with Sesame Carrot Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: Give chicken a dash of flair with a smokey Louisiana spice blend for a melody of robust flavours. Then, don’t stop there. Ramp up your dish with a creamy aioli pear slaw tossed around with cucumber.

